msgctxt "128_Tanimura"
msgid "Hold on... Seems I didn't bring enough money."
msgstr "Espera... Parece que no traje suficiente dinero."

msgctxt "140_峰村七海：源氏名"
msgid "I'm sorry, I must have misheard you. What did you say?"
msgstr "Disculpe, creo que no lo escuche bien. ¿Qué dijo?"

